==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Fyke
<hw>Fyke</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[D. <ets>fuik</ets> a bow
net.]</ety> <def>A long bag net distended by hoops, into which fish can
pass easily, without being able to return; -- called also <altname>fyke
net</altname>.</def> <rj><au>Cozzens.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

